descriptor.name: CamPure Mogra Air Freshener Cone, 60 g
descriptor.long_desc:
CamPure Camphor Mogra Cone is a dual purpose cone that fills the air around you with a delightful, fresh scent, and in some situations the insect repelling properties that can help keep mosquitoes away (or put it in your closet to help protect your clothes). This cone contains no fillers, additives, or bases; just 100% organic raw materials, including camphor with the lowest level of impurities, and high-quality fragrance.

- 100% organic camphor cone that delivers a distinctive and fresh scent for 45 days
- Comes in an attractive 'control release' cloth covering, which enables the scent to spread and quickly neutralize unpleasant odors
- Works great in bathrooms, kitchen cupboards, or even closets, and protects from mold growth
- Known as a healthier alternative to aerosol sprays and fragrances
- This product has a shelf life of 5 years when unopened

About the Brand: Mangalam manufactures pure camphor tablets in various shapes, sizes, and packagings at its technologically advanced manufacturing facility at Kumbhivali, Maharashtra employing over 300 people. The camphor they procure is natural and organic that is widely used for religious purposes, while it has usage far and wide across countries globally.

descriptor.name: Timolong Eye Drops 5 ml
descriptor.short_desc: Ophthalmic Solution, when applied topically on the eye, has the action of reducing elevated as well as normal intraocular pressure, whether or not accompanied by glaucoma. Elevated intraocular pressure is a major risk factor in the pathogenesis of glaucomatous visual field loss. The higher the level of intraocular pressure, the greater the likelihood of glaucomatous visual field loss and optic nerve damage.The onset of reduction in intraocular pressure following administration of eye drop can usually be detected within one-half hour after a single dose. The maximum effect usually occurs in one to two hours and significant lowering of intraocular pressure can be maintained for periods as long as 24 hours with a single dose. Repeated observations over a period of one year indicate that the intraocular pressure-lowering effect of  is well maintained.
descriptor.long_desc: (Timolol maleate ophthalmic solution) is a non-selective beta-adrenergic receptor blocking agent. Its chemical name is (-)-1-(tert-butylamino)-3-[(4-morpholino-1,2,5-thiadiazol-3-yl)oxy]-2-propanol maleate (1:1) (salt). Timolol maleate possesses an asymmetric carbon atom in its structure and is provided as the levo-isomer. TIMOPTIC Ophthalmic Solution is supplied as a sterile, isotonic, buffered, aqueous solution of timolol maleate in two dosage strengths. Each mL of TIMOPTIC 0.25% contains 2.5 mg of timolol (3.4 mg of timolol maleate). The pH of the solution is approximately 7, and the osmolality is 260-340 mOsm/kg. Each mL of TIMOPTIC contains 5 mg of timolol (6.8 mg of timolol maleate). Inactive ingredients: monobasic and dibasic sodium phosphate, sodium hydroxide to adjust pH, and purified water. Benzalkonium chloride 0.01% is added as preservative.

descriptor.name: Timolong Eye Drops 5 ml
descriptor.short_desc: Ophthalmic Solution, when applied topically on the eye, has the action of reducing elevated as well as normal intraocular pressure, whether or not accompanied by glaucoma. Elevated intraocular pressure is a major risk factor in the pathogenesis of glaucomatous visual field loss. The higher the level of intraocular pressure, the greater the likelihood of glaucomatous visual field loss and optic nerve damage.The onset of reduction in intraocular pressure following administration of eye drop can usually be detected within one-half hour after a single dose. The maximum effect usually occurs in one to two hours and significant lowering of intraocular pressure can be maintained for periods as long as 24 hours with a single dose. Repeated observations over a period of one year indicate that the intraocular pressure-lowering effect of  is well maintained.
descriptor.long_desc: (Timolol maleate ophthalmic solution) is a non-selective beta-adrenergic receptor blocking agent. Its chemical name is (-)-1-(tert-butylamino)-3-[(4-morpholino-1,2,5-thiadiazol-3-yl)oxy]-2-propanol maleate (1:1) (salt). Timolol maleate possesses an asymmetric carbon atom in its structure and is provided as the levo-isomer. TIMOPTIC Ophthalmic Solution is supplied as a sterile, isotonic, buffered, aqueous solution of timolol maleate in two dosage strengths. Each mL of TIMOPTIC 0.25% contains 2.5 mg of timolol (3.4 mg of timolol maleate). The pH of the solution is approximately 7, and the osmolality is 260-340 mOsm/kg. Each mL of TIMOPTIC contains 5 mg of timolol (6.8 mg of timolol maleate). Inactive ingredients: monobasic and dibasic sodium phosphate, sodium hydroxide to adjust pH, and purified water. Benzalkonium chloride 0.01% is added as preservative.

@ondc/org/statutory_reqs_packaged_commod.manufacturer_or_packer_address: ITC Quality Care Cell,P.O Box No.592,Bangalore-560005

Protein discs are what happened when the goodness of Trunativ protein met the healthy yet irresistible chocolate discs with impeccable taste and wellness in every bite. These plant-protein chocolate discs are vegan and made with pea protein isolate. These discs are ideal for your everyday protein cravings. They are not only a great substitute for your boring whey protein, but also your daily binge-worthy snack loaded with health and flavor in every bite. These protein chocolate discs are vegan, gluten-free, dairy-free, non-gmo and contain no artificial ingredients, making them ideal for vegans and the ones on a special diet.

- Plant protein chocolate discs that are ideal for your everyday protein cravings
- Made with pea protein isolate that is loaded with health in every bite
- Vegan , gluten-free, dairy free, non GMO and contains no artificial ingredients

About the Brand: Ditch the guilt is a low-carb, high-healthy fat, and high-protein chocolate, with a lot of antioxidants and nutrients. The brand's only mission is to make '100% natural' bean-to-bar chocolate with locally sourced ingredients and no chemicals, added artificial flavors, or preservatives. Their chocolate is perfect in breakfast bowls, a mid-day snack, for your workout buddy, or an after-meal treat.

descriptor.name: Tuskca Vitamin C Amla + Zinc Effervescent Tablet, Orange, 20 tablets
descriptor.short_desc:
- Drop 1 tablet in 200 ml water
- Wait until it has completely dissolved (around 2 minutes), no stirring is necessary
- Enjoy the tasty, fizzy health drink

Country of Origin: India
descriptor.long_desc:
Tuskca Vitamin C Amla + Zinc Effervescent Tablets curated in orange flavor support immune system health and general health and wellbeing. Vitamin C is a powerful antioxidant that can strengthen your body’s natural defenses. These sugar-free effervescent tablets contain antioxidants that are known as molecules that boost the immune system. They do so by protecting cells from harmful molecules called free radicals. Studies show that consuming more vitamin C can increase your blood antioxidant levels by up to 30%. Just one tablet and you are ready with a boost of energy for every possible task.

- Vitamin C effervescent tablets that are suitable for all individuals above 16 years
- Contains antioxidant properties that help to reduce free radical damage to the body cells
- Maintains vitamin C levels in the body and supports immune system health
- Gluten-free, lactose-free, sugar-free, no preservatives, and no yeast

About the Brand: Tuskca came into existence with a brand called Lifezen. Lifezen Healthcare Pvt. Ltd. is a healthcare brand that aims to develop innovative healthcare offerings that provide the ultimate care for life and well-being. They specialize in over-the-counter (OTC) products in different therapeutic segments and aim to become a comprehensive OTC healthcare organization.

descriptor.name: Gerber Cereals Mango & Berry for 2-6 year old kids, 300 g (Bag in Box)
descriptor.long_desc:
With 90 years of global nutrition expertise, Nestle brings you Gerber Cereal with Powerblend- a tasty and special blend of four diverse food groups along with 16 vital nutrients. It contains food groups such as wholegrain oats, legumes, milk, and vegetables designed to meet the nutritional needs of your toddler. Diversity in the diet helps expand a toddler’s food choices for later life. In addition to this Gerber, cereals contain essential nutrients like iron and omega-3 that help support normal cognitive and normal brain development. It’s packed with Immuno-nutrients like vitamins A, C, D, iron, and zinc which help support normal immune system function. It is rich in protein that helps support normal growth in muscle mass.

- Whole grain cereal that helps boost immunity and enhance cognitive skills for your toddler
- Contains a power blend diversity of food groups such as cereal, legumes, milk, and vegetables
- With Immuno-nutrients( Vitamin A, C, D, Iron, and Zinc) to help support normal immune system function
- Diversity in the diet helps expand toddlers' food choices

About the Brand: Like all great brands, Gerber was also born from the desire to solve a genuine problem - a mother's need to nourish her little one. And 90 years later, the brand is still supporting mothers in solving these challenges every single day.

descriptor.name: Baby Dove Rich Moisture Shampoo, 400 ml
descriptor.short_desc:
- Wet your baby’s hair with warm water
- Apply a small amount of this baby shampoo into your hands, gently massage into your baby’s scalp and rinse

Country of Origin: India
descriptor.long_desc:
It’s not just the skin or your baby’s body that needs special care – did you know that the scalp is one of their most sensitive areas, it loses moisture up to 5 times faster after every bath! With a rich, creamy lather of Baby Dove Rich Moisture Shampoo is specially designed to give your baby the sensitive skin and hair care they deserve. Proven to be as gentle as water, it delicately cleanses your baby’s hair without irritating their skin. Made with prebiotic moisturizer and 100% skin-natural nutrients, our no tears shampoo replenishes the scalp with skin-essential nutrients and leaves hair soft and healthy looking. Paediatrician-tested, this shampoo for newborn babies is free from dyes, parabens, phthalates and sulphates. With hypoallergenic, mild cleansers, you can gently cleanse your baby's hair.

- Rich moisture shampoo that is infused with a delicate, comforting scent
- Made with a hypoallergenic formula and formulated with ¼ moisturizing cream
- Provides 100% skin-natural nutrients that help your baby’s scalp retain natural moisture
- Free from dyes, parabens, phthalates and sulphates, certified cruelty-free by PETA

About the Brand: Baby Dove is a range from Hindustan Unilever Limited which was started in 1869. Hindustan Unilever has brands which deliver soaps, detergents, shampoo, tea and many more. Baby Dove is especially launched for babies. They have bathing bars, shampoos, wipes etc made for babies. Their product range includes bathing bars, shampoos, wipes, body lotions etc made for specifically for babies.
